                <p>
                    <lb n="1"/>kō-vicaiya-nanti-vi<supplied reason="omitted">k</supplied>kirama-va<hi rend="grantha">rma</hi><surplus>ma</surplus><choice><orig>r</orig><reg>ṟ</reg></choice>ku yāṇṭu patt’ oṉpat-āvatu
                </p>
                <p>
                    peru
                    <lb n="2" break="no"/>m-paḷḷi-Il vaitta poli-y-ūṭṭu nel mutal iru-<unclear>nū</unclear>ṟṟu
                    <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="line"/>
                </p>
                
