            <div type="translation" resp="part:emfr">
                
                <p n="1">
                    Nineteenth year of the victorious king Nantivikkiramavarmaṉ.<note>Sanskrit Nandivikramavarman.</note>		
                </p>
                
                <p n="1-2">
                    <supplied reason="subaudible">For</supplied> the interest given in the <foreign>perumpaḷḷi</foreign>: a capital of paddy <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> two hundred <gap reason="ellipsis"/>
                </p>
                
